  • Constructor Details

    • AlertPopUp

      public AlertPopUp​(java.lang.String title, java.lang.String msg)
      AlertPopUp constructor initializes the title and message of pop up screen by given parameters. This is called by ViewAdapter which is called by ScreenPlayer in an adapter pattern.
      Parameters:
      title - String value specifying the title of pop up screen.
      msg - String value specifying the message to be shown in pop up screen.
      See Also:
      ViewPlayer, ViewAdapter, ScreenPlayer, PopUpScreen
